name: Mind Flay: Insanity
description:
Devouring Plague transforms your next Mind Flay into Mind Flay: Insanity. Lasts 10 sec.

 Mind Flay: Insanity
Assaults the target's mind with Shadow energy, causing 15,765 Shadow damage over 2.7 sec and slowing their movement speed by 70%.

Generates 16 Insanity over the duration.
